課程說明＞健康行為介入原理與實務














　　本課程旨在探討與評析健康行為介入之理論，教育介入策略與實施過程；學生須參與健康行為介入活動之設計與實作，以發展及提升健康行為介入策略之實作能力。
 
The aim of this course is explore and analyze the theory, strategies and implementation of health behavior intervention. Students are required to involve the intervention design and practice rehearsal for developing and enhancing performance in practice of health behavior intervention. 







